articles.author: Ben Church
articles.title: Indiana Fever win WNBA Commissioner’s Cup without injured Caitlin Clark - CNN
articles.description: Caitlin Clark might have been absent through injury but that didn’t stop the Indiana Fever from winning the WNBA Commissioner’s Cup on Tuesday.
articles.content:
Caitlin Clark might have been absent through injury but that didnt stop the Indiana Fever from winning the WNBA Commissioners Cup on Tuesday.
